-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Parameters:
***********

  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }

  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True

  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True

  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None

    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0

    do_ccd = False

      group = None
    }

      enabled = False
      file = None

      side_chain = True

        reference = None

      }

        exclude_selection = "element H or element D or water"
        chain_similarity_threshold = 0.85
        chain_max_rmsd = 100.
        residue_match_radius = 1000
      }
    }
  }
  output {
    file_name_prefix = None
    model_format = *pdb mmcif
    write_initial_geo_file = False
    write_final_geo_file = False
    write_all_states = false
    write_pkl_stats = False
  }
  pdb_interpretation {
    restraints_library {
      cdl = True
      omega_cdl = False
      rdl = False
      hpdl = False
    }
    sort_atoms = True
    superpose_ideal_ligand = *None all SF4 F3S
    flip_symmetric_amino_acids = False
    disable_uc_volume_vs_n_atoms_check = False
    correct_hydrogens = True
    secondary_structure {
      protein {
        enabled = True
        search_method = *ksdssp mmtbx_dssp from_ca cablam
        distance_ideal_n_o = 2.9
        distance_cut_n_o = 3.5
        remove_outliers = True
        restrain_hbond_angles = True
        helix {
          serial_number = None
          helix_identifier = None
          enabled = True

          sigma = 0.05

            donor = None

          }

          enabled = True
          first_strand = None

            selection = None
            sense = parallel antiparallel *unknown

            bond_start_previous = None
          }

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize
**********
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gather and process all inputs:
******************************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Processing inputs
*****************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parameters:
***********
  model_file = None
  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None
    target_bonds_rmsd = 0.01
    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0
    backbone_sample = True
    use_adp_restraints = True
    atom_radius = 3.0
    do_ss_ideal = False
    do_ccd = False
    rigid_body {
      group = None
    }
    reference_model {
      enabled = False
      file = None
      use_starting_model_as_reference = False
      sigma = 1.0
      limit = 15.0
      hydrogens = False
      main_chain = True

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Parameters:
***********

  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None
    target_bonds_rmsd = 0.01
    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0

    atom_radius = 3.0
    do_ss_ideal = False
    do_ccd = False

      group = None
    }
    reference_model {
      enabled = False
      file = None
      use_starting_model_as_reference = False
      sigma = 1.0
      limit = 15.0
      hydrogens = False
      main_chain = True
      side_chain = True
      fix_outliers = True
      strict_rotamer_matching = False
      auto_shutoff_for_ncs = False
      secondary_structure_only = False
      reference_group {
        reference = None
        selection = None
        file_name = None
      }
      search_options {
        exclude_selection = "element H or element D or water"
        chain_similarity_threshold = 0.85
        chain_max_rmsd = 100.
        residue_match_radius = 1000
      }
    }
  }
  output {
    file_name_prefix = None
    model_format = *pdb mmcif
    write_initial_geo_file = False
    write_final_geo_file = False
    write_all_states = false
    write_pkl_stats = False
  }
  pdb_interpretation {
    restraints_library {
      cdl = True
      omega_cdl = False
      rdl = False
      hpdl = False
    }
    sort_atoms = True
    superpose_ideal_ligand = *None all SF4 F3S
    flip_symmetric_amino_acids = False
    disable_uc_volume_vs_n_atoms_check = False
    correct_hydrogens = True
    secondary_structure {
      protein {
        enabled = True
        search_method = *ksdssp mmtbx_dssp from_ca cablam
        distance_ideal_n_o = 2.9
        distance_cut_n_o = 3.5
        remove_outliers = True
        restrain_hbond_angles = True
        helix {
          serial_number = None
          helix_identifier = None
          enabled = True
          selection = None
          helix_type = *alpha pi 3_10 unknown
          sigma = 0.05
          slack = 0
          top_out = False
          hbond {
            donor = None
            acceptor = None
          }
        }

          enabled = True
          first_strand = None
          sheet_id = None

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize
**********
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gather and process all inputs:
******************************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Processing inputs
*****************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parameters:
***********
  model_file = None
  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize
**********
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gather and process all inputs:
******************************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Processing inputs
*****************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parameters:
***********
  model_file = None
  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None
    target_bonds_rmsd = 0.01
    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0
    backbone_sample = True
    use_adp_restraints = True
    atom_radius = 3.0
    do_ss_ideal = False
    do_ccd = False
    rigid_body {
      group = None
    }
    reference_model {
      enabled = False
      file = None
      use_starting_model_as_reference = False
      sigma = 1.0

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize
**********
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gather and process all inputs:
******************************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Processing inputs
*****************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parameters:
***********
  model_file = None
  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

***********

  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None

  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None
    target_bonds_rmsd = 0.01
    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0

    use_adp_restraints = True

    do_ss_ideal = False
    do_ccd = False

      group = None
    }
    reference_model {
      enabled = False
      file = None
      use_starting_model_as_reference = False

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee

Command line arguments: "48_5t9r_norm_psi_Class50_SVD12_bfac290_4.5A.pdb" "../maps/norm_psi_Class50_SVD12_48_bfac290_4.5A.mrc" "resolution=5" "write_all_states=false" "write_initial_geo_file=False"

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  PHENIX: Python-based Hierarchical ENvironment for Integrated Xtallography
  Version: 1.13
  Release tag: 2998
  Platform: intel-linux-2.6-x86_64
  User: amedee
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize
**********
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gather and process all inputs:
******************************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Processing inputs
*****************
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parameters:
***********
  model_file = None
  map_file = None
  mtz_file = None
  monomers {
    file_name = None
  }
  map_coefficients_label = None
  resolution = 5
  rotamer_restraints = True
  mask_and_he_map = False
  resolution_factor = 0.25
  ncs_constraints = True
  refine_ncs_operators = True
  weight = None
  show_statistics = True
  show_per_residue = True
  dry_run = False
  random_seed = 0
  nproc = 1
  gradients_method = *fd linear quadratic
  scattering_table = *n_gaussian wk1995 it1992 electron neutron
  refinement {
    run = *minimization_global rigid_body local_grid_search morphing \
          simulated_annealing *adp
    morphing = every_macro_cycle *once
    simulated_annealing = every_macro_cycle *once
    max_iterations = 100
    macro_cycles = 5
    high_resolution = None
    target_bonds_rmsd = 0.01
    target_angles_rmsd = 1.0
    backbone_sample = True
    use_adp_restraints = True
    atom_radius = 3.0
    do_ss_ideal = False
    do_ccd = False
    rigid_body {
      group = None
    }
    reference_model {
      enabled = False
      file = None
      use_starting_model_as_reference = False
      sigma = 1.0
      limit = 15.0
      hydrogens = False
      main_chain = True
      side_chain = True
      fix_outliers = True
      strict_rotamer_matching = False
      auto_shutoff_for_ncs = False
      secondary_structure_only = False
      reference_group {
        reference = None
        selection = None
        file_name = None
      }
      search_options {
        exclude_selection = "element H or element D or water"
        chain_similarity_threshold = 0.85
        chain_max_rmsd = 100.
        residue_match_radius = 1000
      }
    }
  }

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
phenix.real_space_refine: tool for extensive real-space refinement of atomic
                          coordinates against provided map

Usage:
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb ccp4_formatted_map.map
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz
  or
  phenix.real_space_refine model.pdb map.mtz label='2FOFCWT,PH2FOFCWT'

Feedback:
  PAfonine@lbl.gov or phenixbb@phenix-online.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  User: amedee
